<h1>Find hexagrams related to a particular hexagram.</h1>
<p>Explore the space of possible evolutions from a given state.</p>
<p>Valid values below are an integer from 1 to 64 (initial hexagram) & a list of integers between 0 and 6 (list of step lengths to include).</p>
<p>A step length is the number of changing lines involved in a transition.</p>
